Cons:. We lost the Premium headphones :(. 
Summary:. If you want more details I wrote a detailed review on my blog.. http://bloguedegeek.net/2008/10/14/microsoft-zune-3g-120go-et-la-mise-a-jour-30-evaluation/. 

